<h1>Trips Dashboard</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
           <div class="col s12">
             <div class="card blue-grey darken-1">
               <div class="card-content white-text">
                 <ul>
                   <li> Average duration of a ride: <%= @trips.average_ride_duration.to_i %> seconds</li>
                   <li> Longest ride: <%= @trips.longest_ride %> seconds</li>
                   <li> Shortest ride: <%= @trips.shortest_ride %> seconds</li>
                   <li> Station with the most rides as a starting place: <%= @trips.most_popular_starting_station.name %></li>
                   <li> Station with the most rides as an ending place: <%= @trips.most_popular_ending_station.name %></li>
                   <li> Month by Month breakdown of number of rides with subtotals for each year: <%# <%= @trips.newest_station %></li>
                   <li> Most ridden bike: <%= @trips.most_ridden_bike[0] %> Total number of rides for that bike: <%= @trips.most_ridden_bike[1] %></li>
                   <li> Least ridden bike: <%= @trips.least_ridden_bike[0] %> Total number of rides for that bike: <%= @trips.least_ridden_bike[1] %></li>
                   <li> Single date with the highest number of trips: <%= @trips.date_most_travelled[0] %> </br> Number of trips: <%= @trips.date_most_travelled[1] %></li>
                   <li> Single date with the lowest number of trips: <%= @trips.date_least_travelled[0] %> </br>Number of trips: <%= @trips.date_least_travelled[1] %></li>
                   <li> Weather on the day with the highest rides: <%# <= @trips.weather_highest_rides></li> %>
                   <li> Weather on the day with the lowest rides: <%# <%= @trips.weather_lowest_rides></li> %>
                 </ul>
               </div>

